ic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-0f8c5de7-a4d6-45bb-afc3-7b39060ca099\">통증과 체형을 한번에!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-f2126aa6-e7a2-4541-acd8-20e56ab73b7d\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-64e5f45e-3669-415e-a670-b28ba537ac5d\">몸과 마음의 균형!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-0c74e1c0-13e7-425c-83be-6d033eb6d973\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-3541cd92-9dbb-417b-85f4-fb5eb601cd7f\">안녕하세요, 이수한의원입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-47e9ee5c-f163-49f5-ae44-9426b67cbd0c\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-16a6eb69-282b-40ed-ac2c-dc07a0b3d90f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-4314ca62-f954-49ef-a2a6-cecc96a25620\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-91a1a8ac-c886-454b-8fed-9d27e6379129\">오늘은 통증해결 한방토크 스물여덟 번째 시간,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-85e6579a-f73a-486a-8714-f40a924c7ada\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#fff8b2;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-40dae844-a050-42dc-a416-6edb1253eca1\"><b>&#x27;가슴 성형 후 결리는 어깨, 둥근 어깨 증후군&#x27;</b></span><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic  se-styl